REST <pre><code>POST /1/aspects

{
  "entity":  "urn:ivcap:artifact:&lt;uuid&gt;",
  "schema":  "urn:ivcap:schema:my-domain:classification.1",
  "content": {
    "class":      "fire-risk",
    "confidence": 0.92
  }
}
</code></pre>

REST <pre><code>POST /1/queues

{
  "name":   "image-processing-pipeline",
  "policy": "urn:ivcap:policy:private"
}
</code></pre>

REST <pre><code>POST /1/queues/urn:ivcap:queue:&lt;uuid&gt;/messages

{
  "content": {
    "artifact": "urn:ivcap:artifact:&lt;uuid&gt;",
    "priority": "high"
  }
}
</code></pre>

CLIREST <pre><code>ivcap order create urn:ivcap:service:&lt;uuid&gt; \
    region="Tasmania-North" \
    threshold=0.05 \
    input-data=urn:ivcap:artifact:&lt;uuid&gt;
</code></pre> <pre><code>POST /1/services/urn:ivcap:service:&lt;uuid&gt;/jobs

{
  "name": "my-fire-analysis-run-1",
  "parameters": [
    { "name": "region",     "value": "Tasmania-North" },
    { "name": "threshold",  "value": "0.05" },
    { "name": "input-data", "value": "urn:ivcap:artifact:&lt;uuid&gt;" }
  ]
}
</code></pre> <p>The platform returns immediately with the job URN and initial status:</p> <pre><code>{
  "id":     "urn:ivcap:job:&lt;uuid&gt;",
  "status": "pending",
  "links":  { "self": "/1/services/.../jobs/urn:ivcap:job:&lt;uuid&gt;" }
}
</code></pre>

CLI (poll)REST (poll)REST (live stream) <pre><code>ivcap order get urn:ivcap:job:&lt;uuid&gt;
</code></pre> <pre><code>GET /1/services/&lt;svcId&gt;/jobs/&lt;jobId&gt;
</code></pre> <pre><code># Server-Sent Events — stream closes when job reaches a terminal state
curl -N -H "Authorization: Bearer &lt;token&gt;" \
  https://api.example.ivcap.net/1/services/&lt;svcId&gt;/jobs/&lt;jobId&gt;/events
</code></pre> <p>Events are emitted as CloudEvents JSON:</p> <pre><code>event: ivcap.job.status
data: {"id":"urn:ivcap:job:&lt;uuid&gt;","status":"executing","timestamp":"..."}

event: ivcap.job.status
data: {"id":"urn:ivcap:job:&lt;uuid&gt;","status":"succeeded","timestamp":"..."}
</code></pre>
